Sure! Here's an implementation of a bubble sort algorithm, which sorts an unsorted list of integers:

```python
def my_sort(lst):
    for i in range(len(lst)):
        for j in range(i+1, len(lst)):
            if lst[i] > lst[j]:
                lst[i], lst[j] = lst[j], lst[i]
    return lst
```
